image_analysis.description: A photograph of a desk setup featuring an Apple iMac computer, a multi-line office telephone, a cup of pens and scissors, and a printer in the background. The desk surface appears to be frosted glass. The iMac screen is dark, reflecting the room. The telephone is a beige 'STARPLUS digital' model with several programmable buttons, some of which have redacted labels. A white charging cable is coiled on the desk.
image_analysis.layout: The iMac is centered in the frame. To the left is a blue and white ceramic pen holder. To the right is a beige office phone. An Epson printer is visible behind the computer.
